<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>in faith • in good faith</xh5><p> <i>in faith—</i>having faith as the basis of a belief: We cannot prove that there is life beyond death; we can only accept it <u>in faith</u>.</p><p> <i>in good faith—</i>with honest belief or intention: Though his statement proved to be untrue, it was made <u>in good faith</u>.</p> </entry>
